COLDWELL BANKER MOUNTAIN WEST REAL ESTATE, INC.

data.description: This classic & timeless 2640 sq.ft house built in 1945 sits high and flat in the hills of Willamina with Grande Rhonde city water. It boasts 3 spacious bedrooms. One on the main floor, providing convenience & accessibility, while the other 2 bedrooms are on the 2nd fl. with all original Knotty Pine, giving style, privacy and separation. There are 2 bathrooms, each located on the first floor and the second floor. Additionally, there is a walk-in pantry and plenty of storage space throughout. Enjoy the view out of the large bay windows in the designated dining room and spacious living room with a cozy pellet stove and enjoy the art of the White Pine mosaic original flooring! The house also includes a basement which can serve for storage, or even a recreational space. Property also includes a lg. detached 2 car garage with a vaulted ceiling extra lg. bonus room upstairs, separate barn with 4 stalls and plenty of room for your tack and feed, and a extra-large workshop!
